scene.message:
Himeno: Oh my, what is it,{nl}
everyone? Did you come to see{nl}
our treasured heirlooms?{waitkey}{clearbox}But sorry, to prevent theft{nl}
we don't open them to the{nl}
public.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I don't even wanna see{nl}
your family's treasures, but{waitkey}{clearbox}"prevent theft" — does that{nl}
mean you're suspecting us?{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: Oh, is that how it{nl}
sounded? How unpleasant, so{nl}
touchy.{waitkey}{clearbox}I didn't mean it that way{nl}
at all.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: {ctl07:1}... I'm feeling{nl}
a little unwell. Might I step{nl}
outside ahead of you?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Argh! This really ticks{nl}
me off!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Just 'cause she's a bit rich,{nl}
who does she think she is!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: You know, Himeno was{nl}
way cuter the way she was{nl}
before.{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: But Maki...{wait_fr:32} you're{nl}
my friend, Maki, but the{nl}
others aren't!{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Yuko Himeno{nl}
Was supposed to be an{nl}
admirable girl working a job{nl}
for her family's sake, but...{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: Maki, won't you stay{nl}
for some tea?{waitkey}{clearbox}There's one extra serving of{nl}
sweets my pastry chef made.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you would, my little{nl}
brothers would be delighted!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Yuko...{wait_fr:32} then I'll{nl}
come by with everyone next{nl}
time.{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: Oh, it's you lot?{wait_fr:32}{nl}
...Fine. Today, as a special{nl}
treat, I'll invite you all in.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Why so sudden{wait_fr:32}...{nl}
I get it.{waitkey}{clearbox}The town's all weird, so{nl}
you're scared, huh?{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: I-it's not that!{waitkey}{clearbox}We've got John the Doberman,{nl}
and Sebastian the butler,{nl}
too!{waitkey}I'm not scared at all!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Heh. Then once all of{nl}
this is resolved, we'll all{nl}
pay you a visit.{waitkey}{ret}
